ent-CMUActionYautjaCreateHumanStabilisingCrystal = Create Human Crystal
    .desc = Spend bracer power to grow a crystal tuned for humans and thralls.
ent-CMUActionYautjaCreateHealingCapsule = Create Healing Capsule
    .desc = Spend bracer power to print a disposable healing capsule.
ent-CMUActionYautjaCreateHuntingTrap = Create Hunting Trap
    .desc = Spend bracer power to print a hunting trap.
ent-CMUActionYautjaOpenMarkPanel = Hunting Marks
    .desc = Mark nearby prey, honored targets, and other Yautja designations.
ent-CMUActionYautjaLinkThrallBracer = Link Thrall Bracer
    .desc = Link your hunting bracer to your marked thrall's bracer.
ent-CMUActionYautjaTransmitThrallMessage = Thrall Transmission
    .desc = Send a private bracer message between hunter and thrall.
ent-CMUActionYautjaToggleThrallBracerLock = Toggle Thrall Bracer Lock
    .desc = Lock or unlock the linked thrall bracer.
ent-CMUActionYautjaStunThrall = Stun Thrall
    .desc = Punish your linked thrall with a remote bracer shock.
ent-CMUActionYautjaSelfDestructThrall = Thrall Self-Destruct
    .desc = Arm or cancel your linked thrall bracer's self-destruct.
ent-CMUActionYautjaRecall = Recall Disc
    .desc = Recall your nearby smart disc to hand.
ent-CMUActionYautjaSelfDestruct = Bracer Self-Destruct
    .desc = Arm or cancel the bracer's delayed self-destruct charge.
ent-CMUActionYautjaToggleCaster = Deploy Caster
    .desc = Deploy or retract your stored shoulder plasma caster.
ent-CMUActionYautjaToggleWristBlades = Deploy Wrist Blades
    .desc = Deploy or retract your stored wrist blades.
ent-CMUActionYautjaToggleScimitar = Deploy Scimitar
    .desc = Deploy or retract your stored combi scimitar.
ent-CMUActionYautjaToggleShield = Deploy Shield
    .desc = Deploy or retract your stored bracer shield.
ent-CMUActionYautjaToggleChainGauntlet = Deploy Gauntlet
    .desc = Deploy or retract your stored chain gauntlet.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoiceClick = Voice: Clicks
    .desc = Emit a burst of Yautja clicks.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoiceRoar = Voice: Roar
    .desc = Let out a hunting roar.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoiceLaugh = Voice: Laugh
    .desc = Play a Yautja laugh.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoiceGrowl = Voice: Growl
    .desc = Make a low Yautja growl.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoicePain = Voice: Pain
    .desc = Play a Yautja pain cry.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoiceDeathCry = Voice: Death Cry
    .desc = Play a Yautja death cry.
ent-CMUActionYautjaVoiceDeathLaugh = Voice: Death Laugh
    .desc = Play the Yautja death laugh.

ent-CMUActionYautjaAbominationRush = Feral Rush
    .desc = Briefly rush forward with predalien speed.
ent-CMUActionYautjaAbominationRoar = Predalien Roar
    .desc = Force nearby hunters out of cloak and empower nearby xenos based on your kills.
ent-CMUActionYautjaAbominationSmash = Feral Smash
    .desc = Slam a nearby target, dealing kill-scaled damage and knocking them down.
ent-CMUActionYautjaAbominationFrenzy = Feral Frenzy
    .desc = Maul a target, or sweep nearby targets when frenzy is set to area mode.
ent-CMUActionYautjaAbominationToggleFrenzy = Toggle Frenzy Mode
    .desc = Switch Feral Frenzy between single-target and area strikes.
